{"type":"tool_call","subtype":"completed","call_id":"call-5eb31380-107f-4e72-b363-3f33d0cbb06e-13\nfc_b7079a1e-7b95-927c-87da-ba6754448a80_4","tool_call":{"readToolCall":{"args":{"path":"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/docs/AI和人类/需求/02-运行时协议.md","offset":1,"limit":50},"result":{"success":{"content":"# 02. 运行时协议\n\n本文描述引擎运行时主链与算法约定。实现落在纯 TypeScript `packages/rpg-engine`，可被 Studio 与未来电话壳共用。\n\n相关：[01](./01-CallCard数据模型.md) · [10](./10-用户与存档.md) · [19](../技术设计文档/19-引擎宿主与会话模型.md) · [50](./50-对话与模型适配.md) · [04](./04-调试器界面需求.md)\n\n## 1. 主链\n\n```text\n选定 User → 加载 PlayerProfile\nCallIntent\n  → CallCardResolver\n  → 绑定 CallCardInstance；beginCall → CallSession（frozenCard + ComposeScene）\n  → ContextComposer（只读；promptScenes + 本地时间）\n  → DialogueAdapter.start(DialogueSessionSpec)\n  → … DialogueEvent …（工具只登记 RuntimeExitCandidate）\n  → session.ended + phoneFlags\n  → Story：OutcomeEvaluator → ExitSelector → EffectExecutor（+ Sink）→ 可选 MemoryCommit\n  → Free：FreeCallPostPipeline（MemoryCommit → 有候选则 ExitSelector → Effect）\n  → save Profile；WET / logs\n```\n\n铁律：\n\n- 经历态只读写 **当前 PlayerProfile**；会话态在 **CallSession**（见 [19](../技术设计文档/19-引擎宿主与会话模型.md)）。\n- **通话中不执行**推进类 effect；禁止 onConnect 写记忆。\n- **active ≠ completed**；`call.ended ≠ story.card.completed`。\n- Story 挂机后 Effect 可跨角色 `patch_memory`；Free 走总管线而非强制 exits。\n- 对话通道见 [50](./50-对话与模型适配.md)。\n\n## 2. CallIntent（逻辑输入）\n\n引擎不依赖话机 GPIO；只认逻辑意图：\n\n```ts\ntype CallIntent =\n  | { kind: \"user_dial\"; agentId: string }\n  | { kind: \"agent_outbound\"; agentId: string; instanceId?: string }\n  | { kind: \"redial\"; agentId: string }           // 来自重播槽\n  | { kind: \"simulate_start\"; cardId: string }    // 调试器：从某卡强制开始\n```\n\n## 3. CallCardResolver\n\n### 3.1 输入\n\n- `intent: CallIntent`\n- `board: CallCardBoard`\n- `package: StoryPackage`\n- `redialSlot?: { agentId: string; cardId?: string }`","isEmpty":false,"exceededLimit":false,"totalLines":221,"fileSize":9517,"path":"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/docs/AI和人类/需求/02-运行时协议.md","readRange":{"startLine":1,"endLine":50},"relatedCursorRulePaths":[],"relatedCursorRules":[]}}},"hookAdditionalContexts":[],"toolCallId":"call-5eb31380-107f-4e72-b363-3f33d0cbb06e-13\nfc_b7079a1e-7b95-927c-87da-ba6754448a80_4","startedAtMs":"1784787308943","completedAtMs":"1784787309434"},"model_call_id":"f5e7fb25-1bbd-4e66-b4fe-9682829ca28d-3-pqqd","session_id":"bbabb225-f4cb-4520-b3f9-0dcbbd20fe8e","timestamp_ms":1784787309434}
