ills/general-batch-exe/bin/gbx.js --exFile docs/AI和人类/里程碑/v2.0/语音留言改造_执行索引.md --workdir . --dry-run`  ","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":79,"content":"> **需求真源：** [语音留言改造需求.md](./语音留言改造需求.md)","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":81,"content":"本文回答：**语音留言从 Effect 桩改为 `cardKind=voicemail` + 物化管线**按什么顺序做、做到哪算完。","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":91,"content":"| `cardKind=voicemail` + `mailbox_open` + 强制 `playback_only` | 引擎内置 LLM |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":93,"content":"| VoicemailMaterialize + 外置生成/未读端口 | 隐式扫 transcript |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":94,"content":"| 废弃 `create_voicemail`（引擎+Studio） | 完整调试台大改版（仅最小信箱路径） |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":102,"content":"V2-VM-3    validatePackage：voicemail 强制 mode；拒绝 create_voicemail；单测","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":105,"content":"V2-VM-6    VoicemailMaterializePipeline + Host 挂接（plan 终态后）","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":108,"content":"V2-VM-9    Studio：Effect 下拉删 create_voicemail；attach/schedule 摘要「进信箱」","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":111,"content":"V2-VM-12   废弃 create_voicemail 全仓清理（Sink/测试/旧面板文件）","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":134,"content":"| ⬜ | V2-VM-1 | **文档骨架**：按需求 §3 回写需求 01/02 中 CardKind、EntryMode、attach/schedule 分流与废弃 create_voicemail 段落 | 人工核对链接 |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":135,"content":"| ⬜ | V2-VM-2 | **Schema**：`voicemail` / `mailbox_open`；telephony 槽字段与未读推导；导出门面 | npm run quality:engine |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":136,"content":"| ⬜ | V2-VM-3 | **校验**：voicemail 强制 playback_only+mailbox_open+deny_all；create_voicemail error；VOICEMAIL_* 单测 | npm run quality:engine |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":141,"content":"| ⬜ | V2-VM-8 | **Studio 卡种**：下拉「语音留言」；interactionMode/entryMode 锁定 disable | npm run quality:studio |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":142,"content":"| ⬜ | V2-VM-9 | **Studio Effect**：删除 create_voicemail 面板与枚举；attach/schedule 人话标明进信箱 | npm run quality:studio |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":143,"content":"| ⬜ | V2-VM-10 | **样例包**：`lanxing_voicemail` 改 cardKind；callback 出口 attach 替代 create_voicemail；validate 绿 | npm run quality:engine |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":144,"content":"| ⬜ | V2-VM-11 | **调试/听完路径**：信箱最小 UI 或 Host 单测证明 mailbox_open → Outcome → exits | npm run quality:engine |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":145,"content":"| ⬜ | V2-VM-12 | **全仓清理**：Sink/旧测试/旧面板文件去掉 create_voicemail 新写路径 | npm run quality:engine · npm run quality:studio |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":172,"content":"- [ ] Studio 无 create_voicemail；字段锁定  ","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":184,"content":"| 任务 | 语音留言改造需求 |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":200,"content":"- **先校验后分流**：未 VM-3 不要宣称旧包已拒 `create_voicemail`。  ","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false}]},{"file":"docs/AI和人类/里程碑/v2.0/语音留言改造需求.md","matches":[{"lineNumber":1,"content":"# Studio V2.0 · 语音留言改造需求","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":4,"content":"> **性质：** 将「语音留言」从独立 Effect 桩（`create_voicemail`）收束为专用 **CallCard 种类**（`cardKind=voicemail`），复用挂卡 / 延迟调度 / 出口 Effect，并明确引擎外 LLM 物化与壳侧未读同步。  ","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":5,"content":"> **执行索引：** [语音留言改造_执行索引.md](./语音留言改造_执行索引.md)  ","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":16,"content":"| **没有** `cardKind=voicemail`；样例「语音留言」卡实为普通 `story` + `realtime_dialogue` | 作者与调试者误以为「挂这张卡 = 听留言」 |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":17,"content":"| 留言能力落在 Effect `create_voicemail`：只写 `telephony.voicemails[]` stub，真播归壳 | 编辑器只有参数面板；**卡种下拉无「留言卡」**；引擎无专用会话语义 |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":18,"content":"| 样例出口仅 `create_voicemail`（带 `cardId`），**不** `attach_call_card` | 画布边指向留言卡，但运行时**不会**把该卡挂进 Board；拓扑与执行脱节 |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":28,"content":"       （Effect 下拉不再提供 create_voicemail）","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":35,"content":"plan 终态之后：VoicemailMaterializePipeline（显式 Host 阶段）","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":41,"content":"听留言：打开信箱 → beginCall（entryMode=mailbox_open，playback_only）","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":58,"content":"A 契约：CardKind 增加 voicemail；entryMode 增加 mailbox_open；废弃 create_voicemail","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":60,"content":"C 物化：显式 VoicemailMaterializePipeline + 外置生成端口 + 未读通知端口","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":61,"content":"D Studio：卡种/锁定字段 UI；Effect 下拉去掉 create_voicemail；挂卡可指向留言卡","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":82,"content":"| 细化修改 7 | Effect 面板已有 `create_voicemail` → 本批删除该选项与面板 |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":96,"content":"| `entryMode` | **仅** `mailbox_open`（界面文案「信箱打开」）；Studio disable；校验 error 若不符 |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":119,"content":"| `create_voicemail` | — | **废弃**：Schema 拒识或 validate error；Studio 下拉删除 |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":123,"content":"### 3.4 物化阶段（VoicemailMaterializePipeline）","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":162,"content":"| 入口 | 用户/调试打开信箱条目 → `beginCall`，`entryMode=mailbox_open` |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":182,"content":"| 卡种下拉 | 增加「语音留言」→ `voicemail` |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":184,"content":"| Effect 下拉 | **删除** `create_voicemail` 及专属面板 |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":201,"content":"| 废弃 effect | `outcome.ts` / Sink 媒介表去掉 `create_voicemail`；旧包 validate 报错并指引改 attach |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":215,"content":"  → VoicemailMaterializePipeline（出栈 × N）","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":225,"content":"- **历史 `create_voicemail` Sink 分支：** 删除或改为「仅兼容读旧 stub，不新写」——本批推荐 **直接废弃**，样例迁移后无旧路径","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":233,"content":"| 调试按 story 卡 beginCall 留言卡 | 错；必须 mailbox_open / 信箱入口 |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":240,"content":"- [ ] Schema / 校验：`voicemail` + `mailbox_open` + `playback_only` 强制；非法组合 error  ","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":243,"content":"- [ ] Studio：无 `create_voicemail` 选项；voicemail 卡字段锁定  ","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":256,"content":"| 需求 01 | CardKind / EntryMode；废弃 create_voicemail；挂卡分流表 |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":259,"content":"| 需求 08 | VOICEMAIL_* 校验码（kind/mode 不匹配、create_voicemail 废弃等） |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false}]},{"file":"docs/AI和人类/里程碑/v2.0/细化修改7_需求.md","matches":[{"lineNumber":74,"content":"| `create_voicemail` | 创建语音信箱 | B | `agentId?`(默当前) · `cardId?` · `topicHint?` | 角色/卡下拉 + 文本 |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":142,"content":"| `create_voicemail` | 生成一条语音信箱桩，真正播放由电话壳执行 |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false}]},{"file":"docs/AI和人类/里程碑/v2.0/细化修改7_执行索引.md","matches":[{"lineNumber":121,"content":"      set_world_fact / create_voicemail / play_system_prompt）+ keep_card_pending 无参说明","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":150,"content":"| ✅ | V2-S7-2 | **B 类简单面板**：schedule_call_card / create_research_commitment / update_user_profile / set_world_fact / create_voicemail / play_system_prompt 专属字段面板；keep_card_pending 无参说明；`ExitEffectsMockList` 改为按 effect 分发到 `com/effects/` 子组件 | npm run quality:studio |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false}]},{"file":"docs/AI和人类/sudioV2.0版本/需求/引擎小改和增强计划.md","matches":[{"lineNumber":488,"content":"- `create_voicemail`","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false}]},{"file":"docs/AI和人类/需求/02-运行时协议.md","matches":[{"lineNumber":184,"content":"| `create_voicemail` | 写入 mock `voicemails[]`（壳侧真执行） |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false}]},{"file":"docs/AI和人类/技术设计文档/07-壳嵌入与导出契约.md","matches":[{"lineNumber":123,"content":"| create_voicemail | 真信箱 |","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false}]}],"totalLines":64,"totalMatchedLines":64,"clientTruncated":false,"ripgrepTruncated":false}}}}}},"hookAdditionalContexts":[],"toolCallId":"call-385f2dcd-2cec-41ae-baf5-74d87d45dc89-14\nfc_ff1ea4d2-862f-9676-aebb-3638e9fa3f97_0","startedAtMs":"1784787324479","completedAtMs":"1784787325072"},"model_call_id":"f5e7fb25-1bbd-4e66-b4fe-9682829ca28d-4-f8q0","session_id":"bbabb225-f4cb-4520-b3f9-0dcbbd20fe8e","timestamp_ms":1784787325043}
{"type":"tool_call","subtype":"completed","call_id":"call-385f2dcd-2cec-41ae-baf5-74d87d45dc89-15\nfc_ff1ea4d2-862f-9676-aebb-3638e9fa3f97_1","tool_call":{"readToolCall":{"args":{"path":"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/docs/AI和人类/需求/02-运行时协议.md","offset":50,"limit":40},"result":{"success":{"content":"- `redialSlot?: { agentId: string; cardId?: string }`\n\n### 3.2 规则（v1）\n\n在 **当前 Profile** 上：\n\n1. `simulate_start`：直接激活指定 `cardId` 的新 Instance（或已有 pending），忽略日常优先级。\n2. `redial`：若槽指向 `cardId`，优先激活该 Definition 在目标角色上的对应 pending；若无 pending，可按包配置挂卡再激活（校验器应警告「重播未挂卡」）。\n3. `user_dial` / `agent_outbound`：\n   - **有效可拨**：`effectiveDialable = !def.isNarrativeOnly && ((def.dialable === true) || (runtime?.unlocked === true))`。\n   - 若意图为 `user_dial` 且 `!effectiveDialable` → `CHARACTER_NOT_DIALABLE`；`agent_outbound` / `simulate_start` 仍允许（**narrative-only 除外**：外呼亦拒绝，除非调试 force）。\n   - 在目标 `pending` 中筛选 `entryMode` 匹配的 Instance（拨号：`inbound_user_dial|either`（及 `inbound` 别名）；外呼：`outbound_auto|either`（及 `outbound` / `agent_outbound` 别名））。**`redialSlot` 仅作优先，不过 mode 则跳过**（见 `pickPendingForIntent`）。\n   - 多张：比 `priority` 降序，同 priority 取 **createdAt 最新**。\n   - 无匹配 pending：使用该角色 **FreeCallCard**（Session.`packageId = \"__free__\"`）。\n4. 若该角色已有 `active` 且未结束：冲突（占线）。\n5. ActiveStoryLock：按 [19 §8.4](../技术设计文档/19-引擎宿主与会话模型.md) 决策表（soft/hard × blockedPolicy）。\n\n### 3.3 输出\n\n```ts\ninterface ResolveResult {\n  instance: CallCardInstance\n  definition: CallCardDefinition\n  source: \"story_pending\" | \"free\" | \"redial\" | \"simulate\"\n}\n```\n\n## 4. 会话期行为（逻辑）\n\n| interactionMode | 引擎关注点 |\n|-----------------|------------|\n| `realtime_dialogue` | Composer + toolPolicy；经 DialogueAdapter 会话；等待结束 + Outcome |\n| `playback_only` | 等待 `playback_completed` / `playback_skipped` / `hangup_early` / `missed` |\n| `hybrid` | 先播放阶段，再进入对话阶段 |\n\n通道（Realtime/文本/Manual）由 Adapter 决定，见 [50](./50-对话与模型适配.md)。\n\n## 5. Outcome 构造\n\n见 [01 §9](./01-CallCard数据模型.md)。v1 由调试器 / ManualEvaluator 填写；须符合同一 Outcome schema。","isEmpty":false,"exceededLimit":false,"totalLines":221,"fileSize":9517,"path":"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/docs/AI和人类/需求/02-运行时协议.md","readRange":{"startLine":50,"endLine":89},"relatedCursorRulePaths":[],"relatedCursorRules":[]}}},"hookAdditionalContexts":[],"toolCallId":"call-385f2dcd-2cec-41ae-baf5-74d87d45dc89-15\nfc_ff1ea4d2-862f-9676-aebb-3638e9fa3f97_1","startedAtMs":"1784787324906","completedAtMs":"1784787325339"},"model_call_id":"f5e7fb25-1bbd-4e66-b4fe-9682829ca28d-4-f8q0","session_id":"bbabb225-f4cb-4520-b3f9-0dcbbd20fe8e","timestamp_ms":1784787325272}
