{"type":"tool_call","subtype":"started","call_id":"call-7173e470-1b0e-4b0e-8dec-879d7126d57b-23\nfc_0a7f42bc-2324-9a26-8161-59cab3c276f5_1","tool_call":{"editToolCall":{"args":{"path":"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/docs/AI和人类/需求/02-运行时协议.md","streamContent":"相关：[01](./01-CallCard数据模型.md) · [10](./10-用户与存档.md) · [19](../技术设计文档/19-引擎宿主与会话模型.md) · [50](./50-对话与模型适配.md) · [04](./04-调试器界面需求.md) · [语音留言改造需求](../里程碑/v2.0/语音留言改造需求.md)\n\n## 1. 主链\n\n```text\n选定 User → 加载 PlayerProfile\nCallIntent\n  → CallCardResolver\n  → 绑定 CallCardInstance；beginCall → CallSession（frozenCard + ComposeScene）\n  → ContextComposer（只读；promptScenes + 本地时间）\n  → DialogueAdapter.start(DialogueSessionSpec)\n  → … DialogueEvent …（工具只登记 RuntimeExitCandidate）\n  → session.ended + phoneFlags\n  → Story：OutcomeEvaluator → ExitSelector → EffectExecutor（+ Sink）→ 可选 MemoryCommit\n  → Free：FreeCallPostPipeline（MemoryCommit → 有候选则 ExitSelector → Effect）\n  → （若 GenStack 非空）VoicemailMaterializePipeline（plan 终态之后；外置生成端口）\n  → save Profile；WET / logs\n```\n\n铁律：\n\n- 经历态只读写 **当前 PlayerProfile**；会话态在 **CallSession**（见 [19](../技术设计文档/19-引擎宿主与会话模型.md)）。\n- **通话中不执行**推进类 effect；禁止 onConnect 写记忆。\n- **active ≠ completed**；`call.ended ≠ story.card.completed`。\n- Story 挂机后 Effect 可跨角色 `patch_memory`；Free 走总管线而非强制 exits。\n- **`cardKind=voicemail` 永不进 `Board.pending`**；进信箱靠 attach/schedule 分流 + 物化（见 §8.4–§8.5）。\n- 对话通道见 [50](./50-对话与模型适配.md)。\n\n## 2. CallIntent（逻辑输入）\n\n引擎不依赖话机 GPIO；只认逻辑意图：\n\n```ts\ntype CallIntent =\n  | { kind: \"user_dial\"; agentId: string }\n  | { kind: \"agent_outbound\"; agentId: string; instanceId?: string }\n  | { kind: \"redial\"; agentId: string }           // 来自重播槽\n  | { kind: \"simulate_start\"; cardId: string }    // 调试器：从某卡强制开始\n  | { kind: \"mailbox_open\"; agentId: string; voicemailId: string; cardId: string }\n  // 信箱打开：听已物化留言；Resolver / beginCall 绑定该 voicemail 卡（entryMode=mailbox_open）\n```\n\n**听留言路径（钉死）：** 用户/调试打开信箱条目 → `mailbox_open` → `beginCall`（`frozenCard` = 该 `cardKind=voicemail` 卡，`interactionMode=playback_only`）→ 播槽内 text/audioRef → Outcome（`voicemail_listened` / `playback_completed` / `playback_skipped` 等）→ ExitSelector → 该卡 `exits`。**不推荐**壳自播完只打 flag、Host 另写无 Session 的 exits 捷径。"}},"hookAdditionalContexts":[],"toolCallId":"call-7173e470-1b0e-4b0e-8dec-879d7126d57b-23\nfc_0a7f42bc-2324-9a26-8161-59cab3c276f5_1","startedAtMs":"1784787397228"},"model_call_id":"f5e7fb25-1bbd-4e66-b4fe-9682829ca28d-6-i91m","session_id":"bbabb225-f4cb-4520-b3f9-0dcbbd20fe8e","timestamp_ms":1784787397175}
